### - Input: Organization registration date / Дата реєстрації організації: 
Consists of:    
	- Input select of the Year
	- Input select of the month
	- Input select of the day

1. Validation:
	- Dates must correspond to the number of days in the month, considering leap years.
	- Input select must be filled in sequentially: year, then month, then day.
Access to the next Input select opens after selecting the previous one, as shown here: https://dpsdealers.com/vehicle-search/

Scenario: Validate the registration date input field
    Given the user is on the registration page
    When the user selects a registration date
    Then the year select should allow selection up to 100 years ago from the current date
    And the month select should allow selection of any month
    And the day select should allow selection of any day

Scenario Outline: Validate the registration date input field with various dates
    Given the user is on the registration page
    When the user selects a registration date "<registration_date>"
    Then the registration date "<registration_date>" should be within the allowed range
    Examples:
        | registration_date   |
        | 26 March 1924       |  # 100 years ago
        | 26 March 2024       |  # current date

2. Error handling:
	- If the input field becomes active and then becomes inactive and does not contain any symbols, this should be indicated in the error field when the input field becomes inactive.
Specify the text in the error field - These fields are required / Ці поля є обов’язковими для заповнення.

