## Acceptance Criteria
1. If the organization representative enters valid data into the forms and submits the form, he should see a Pop-up with text according to the layout.
Where the “Accept” / "Зрозуміло" button leads to the Main Page, and the “Contact” / "Зв'язатись" button leads to the Contact page.
2. If the organization representative enters valid data in the forms and submits the form, the application is to be sent to the SuperAdmin for consideration.
3. An organization representative can not apply if he has at least one verification error.
